TO DO ************* change docs to reflect new impl The main class of the package. This is created by FileRegistryFactoryMac, and on Mac, all calls to the FileRegistry singleton will be delegated to this class. This class loads the appropriate native code shared library.
If Internet Config is installed, some calls are delegated to an IConfigMRJ object; otherwise, those calls are delegated to a ConfigListFile object.
Some other calls are delegated to an AppFinderMRJ object, as well as to native code via AppUtilsMRJ.
